net.sourceforge.htmlunit.corejs.javascript.tools.debugger
Class Main

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.htmlunit.corejs.javascript.tools.debugger.Main

public class Main
extends java.lang.Object

Rhino script debugger main class. This class links together a debugger object (Dim) and a debugger GUI object (SwingGui).
